<title>Sioni Haya Kwa Bwana TZR82</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sioni haya kwa Bwana
 Kwake nitang'ara!
 Mti wake sitakana,
 Ni neno imara!

[V2]
 Msalaba ndio asili ya mema,
 Nikatua mzigo hapo;
 Nina uzima, furaha daima,
 Njoni kafurahini papo.

[V3]
 Kama kiti chake vivyo
 Ni yake ahadi,
 Alivyowekewa navyo
 Kamwe havirudi.

[V4]
 Bwana wangu, tena Mungu
 Ndilo lake jina!
 Hataacha roho yangu
 Wala kunikana.

[V5]
 Atakiri langu jina,
 Mbele za Babaye,
 Anipe pahali tena
 Mbinguni nikae.</lyrics>
</song>